Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.84,0:01:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個土地才是我的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.02,0:02:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝福奢望野心的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十九話\N雷太郎的野望\N被禁止王國的幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊豆真是個不錯的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好興奮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.64,0:02:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在這種地方好好的玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等 等一下 不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊的妹妹\N應該快來接我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎各位來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家的事我常聽我哥哥提起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.21,0:02:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得真像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 小薰小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等 等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.13,0:03:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要麻煩您照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經很久沒有休假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊豆是個很好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.87,0:03:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好的玩個一兩個禮拜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩個半個月吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了 一個月！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的診療所沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給玄齊大夫 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真的有點興致勃勃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺不知道會是什麼臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在帶你們到我家之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何想讓你們見一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎小少爺在需要人照顧時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙親都去逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.95,0:04:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五歲的時候 就成為那間房子的主人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在五歲的時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏能看到的土地 全部是少爺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你一生中都沒緣份的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有的東西都是小少爺的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我說幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想早一點學劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.17,0:05:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要到什麼時候才能找到師父呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是…由太郎小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去給我找來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要比死去的父親還差的劍豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您死去的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.01,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人們稱為伊豆的雷神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他的技術相比的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能找到還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.99,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能像父親一樣的師父是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要變得跟我父親一樣的強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到明天為止給我找來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是很拽的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是親戚嗎 好好去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你一直煮好吃的飯菜給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.15,0:05:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這一位就是我常跟你說的劍豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.16,0:05:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強得會讓你嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長得不是像女孩子一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 如果有相當的技術的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上讓我見識見識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那把刀 將那吊燈打下來讓我看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.45,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親..父親用被稱為雷神的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在15歲的時候 將那吊燈打落下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你能做同樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就有資格成為我的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常的不湊巧…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.44,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生並不想成為劍術的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你住其他的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並給你傭人使喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是馬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要馬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個..我不知道小少爺什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經忍不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再侮辱劍心一句看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明神禰彥就不饒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你..你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕視劍心的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無論如何不會原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再等100年 也沒有學劍…術的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你..要對小少爺做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是禰彥所說的事是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.69,0:07:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的身心皆還未成熟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對師父也倨傲神氣支使人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也學不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.66,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學劍術 就是要從心裏開始學起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你的師父是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.10,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的你絕對沒辦法成為強者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在對什麼人說話….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是我的房子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是主人！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺 馬已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是散步的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你說…小少爺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙好沒水準！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.03,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？不是跟某位很像嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不喜歡認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常的傲慢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開 開玩笑！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還有一點尿騷味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被大人服侍著長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會那麼的傲慢自大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心地卻是非常正直的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有好的師父教導他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎少爺一定能成為強者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.16,0:08:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小少爺 危險！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住嘴！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 第一次被那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小..小少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不要殺他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那麼大間的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.39,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以拿到很多的贖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了了…小少爺.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太無禮了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.87,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道我是誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要溜走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死去的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被為雷神的劍術高超者…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.37,0:10:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支劍如閃電般讓這世界裂開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如閃電般…閃電般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為…什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要無意義的殺生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.04,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我知道你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.08,0:10:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石動…雷十太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石動雷十太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我父親的再生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太師父\N從現在起要住在這屋子裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是少有的劍術高手\N而且是我的恩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.47,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不要怠慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要跟我父親一樣的尊重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可無理 否則我絕不原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷太郎師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷太郎師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.51,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太師父\N什麼時候要開始練習呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在很想開始練習…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要喋喋不休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想成為強者的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.60,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍術只有殺人和被殺而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹刀是小孩子的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再拿了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經是我輩的孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是真古流的四天王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真古流？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太大人的同志…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從現在開始\N是真古流的一員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.94,0:12:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要以雷十太大人的同志為榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…好快樂喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來伊豆還是要洗溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.73,0:13:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對身體很好還可以消除疲勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧 劍哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得好像有去工作一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.34,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有去採集草藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不可以偷看我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要偷看的話\N也要看值得看的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.03,0:14:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 被說成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這麼說反而想去偷看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈..想得美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.81,0:14:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有男的在旁邊\N你認為我們會脫光光嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太狡猾了 太狡猾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪邊狡猾呢…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點把衣服曬乾就要下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支太刀….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來歷不明 隱藏在黑暗裏的石動雷十太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是何人物…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼由太郎從那時候開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已完全聽雷十太大人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一些來歷不明的傢伙\N也都住進房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來歷不明的傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是年輕的男子\N在大房子繞一圈後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.24,0:15:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連冢山家的傳家之寶\N都私自拿出去賣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可這樣！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那些錢買了一大堆的刀槍來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論什麼都是..\N真古流所需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真古流…！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.42,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.36,0:15:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎捲進了不尋常的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要盡快把由太郎少爺\N從雷十太的身邊帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先暫時讓他住在花婆婆這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真行 飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守住這個山崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼王國就完成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷十太大人已控制那小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.43,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那男的真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的殺人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 我應該有叫你走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.73,0:17:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支刀不適合由太郎少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你都是一個人在練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是…雷十太嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你連師父的腳都不及還這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.91,0:17:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想跟師父一樣的強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是特別前來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師父！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我回大屋子去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可…可是！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有話對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有話對我說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得這明治時代怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍術用竹刀來揮著玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時代已經墜落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.58,0:18:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在國民平等之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在武士的靈魂已死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.86,0:18:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的命\N永遠跟這支劍共存著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎你加入我們的真古流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想借重傳說的殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.18,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們以前都是武士\N以殺人活過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治時期後實施廢刀令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我們丟掉劍不如叫我們去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代要我們丟棄我們的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.19,0:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這時候\N能成為一般的市民嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣的話….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要創造自己的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.13,0:18:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們這裏邀集所有精練劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並使殺人劍術\N能發揮到極限的人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在伊豆創造出\N最強的集團真古流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備迎接政府強烈的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候伊豆的深崖\N會成為我們很好的城壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會練就一身\N不畏西洋槍炮的劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.99,0:19:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓那洋裏洋氣的政府知道\N日本古來的武術才是最強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那會讓住在這裏\N無辜的百姓犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家不是有教我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.04,0:19:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者因為弱者的犧牲\N才能君臨天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是\N以殺人劍而生存的拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.51,0:19:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那最強的劍助我們建設王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.12,0:19:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是保護弱小窮苦的民眾的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是為了一個人\N而建設王國的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也要覺醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人考慮該怎麼生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡扯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰鬥的話我們的人生也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人者應該忘記你的存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.71,0:20:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你們不覺醒的話 小生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.58,0:20:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算不殺你們\N而把你們給消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.39,0:20:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣..\N你已知道所有的密秘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從全國各地所挑選出來的好手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的同志真古流四天王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是拔刀齊也沒辦法贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好..好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.94,0:21:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.89,0:21:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能封閉你的神速\N你也會沒有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧 拔刀齊

